{"inkVersion":21,"root":[[{"->":"confucius_intro"},["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"confucius_intro":[["^Confucius: Welcome, traveler, to the Hall of Rites. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n","^Confucius: Here we seek not only wisdom, but harmony between Heaven, Earth, and humanity. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n","^Confucius: Tell me, seeker—will you walk the path of li (ritual and order), or follow only your own heart’s desire? ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n",["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.15.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^To follow li, the way of order. ","#","^moral:order:+1","/#",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.16.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^To follow my own heart’s desire. ","#","^moral:chaos:+1","/#",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.15.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"order"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"order","re":true},"/ev","^Confucius: Ah, noble choice! Ritual cultivates respect, and respect nurtures virtue. ","#","^speaker:confucius ","/#","#","^sticker:order_scroll","/#","\n","^Confucius: Yet tell me—do you follow li because you fear punishment, or because you revere harmony itself? ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-0.26.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^Out of fear of punishment. ","#","^moral:chaos:+1","/#",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-0.26.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^Out of reverence for harmony. ","#","^moral:order:+1","/#",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-0.26.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"chaos"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"chaos","re":true},"/ev","^Confucius: Then your virtue is shallow, for it bends only when threatened. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n","^Confucius: True harmony must spring from the heart, not from fear. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n",{"->":"story_end"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-0.26.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"order"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"order","re":true},"/ev","^Confucius: Indeed! To act with reverence is to align oneself with Heaven’s way. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n","^Confucius: You walk the path of the junzi—the noble person. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n",{"->":"story_end"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.16.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"chaos"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"chaos","re":true},"/ev","^Confucius: Many pursue desire—for it is easy, immediate, and sweet to the tongue. ","#","^speaker:confucius ","/#","#","^sticker:chaos_flame","/#","\n","^Confucius: But tell me—does desire lead to harmony, or to disorder? ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n",[["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-1.26.0.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-0","flg":18},{"s":["^It leads to harmony. ","#","^moral:order:+1","/#",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-1.26.1.$r1"},{"temp=":"$r"},"str",{"->":".^.s"},[{"#n":"$r1"}],"/str","/ev",{"*":".^.^.c-1","flg":18},{"s":["^It leads to disorder. ","#","^moral:chaos:+1","/#",{"->":"$r","var":true},null]}],{"c-0":["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-1.26.c-0.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.0.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"order"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"order","re":true},"/ev","^Confucius: If one’s desires are virtuous, then yes—desire and harmony may unite. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n","^Confucius: Yet such a heart is rare, requiring constant cultivation. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n",{"->":"story_end"},{"#f":5}],"c-1":["ev",{"^->":"confucius_intro.0.c-1.26.c-1.$r2"},"/ev",{"temp=":"$r"},{"->":".^.^.1.s"},[{"#n":"$r2"}],"\n","ev",{"VAR?":"chaos"},1,"+",{"VAR=":"chaos","re":true},"/ev","^Confucius: Then you see clearly. For when desire rules unchecked, families break, kingdoms fall, and harmony shatters. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n","^Confucius: Beware the path of chaos—it is wide, but it ends in ruin. ","#","^speaker:confucius","/#","\n",{"->":"story_end"},{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":5}]}],{"#f":1}],"story_end":["done",{"#f":1}],"global decl":["ev",0,{"VAR=":"order"},0,{"VAR=":"chaos"},"/ev","end",null],"#f":1}],"listDefs":{}}